videos.headline: Ehlinger powers into end zone for TD
videos.description: Texas goes right down the field on its first drive leading to a Sam Ehlinger 2-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Texas forces the fumble and pounces on it
videos.description: Georgia running back D'Andre Swift gets the ball stripped and it is recovered by Texas' Gerald Wilbon.

videos.headline: Ehlinger's second rushing TD increases Texas' lead
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger avoids a tackle in the backfield and squeezes his way into the end zone for his second rushing score of the day.

videos.headline: Georgia gets on the board with Herrien TD
videos.description: Jake Fromm throws a dart to Brian Herrien who hauls it in and scores a 17-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ridley stays on feet and gets big gain
videos.description: Georgia's Riley Ridley stays up after a tackle attempt, then turns it into a big gain.

videos.headline: Herman: Can't settle for field goals in red zone
videos.description: Texas coach Tom Herman likes his team's first-half performance but thought it could have been more efficient with its red-zone chances.

videos.headline: Ehlinger's two rushing TDs give Longhorns lead at halftime
videos.description: Texas quarterback Sam Ehlinger has two rushing touchdowns as the Longhorns lead Georgia 20-7 at halftime of the Allstate Sugar Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ehlinger’s two rushing TDs give Longhorns lead at halftime) 2019/1/1 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Texas picks off Fromm for 2nd turnover of the night
videos.description: Jake Fromm tries to go deep but is picked off by Texas' P.J. Locke III who returns it 22 yards.

videos.headline: Texas' Johnson high points ball for huge gain
videos.description: Texas wide receiver Collin Johnson uses his height and goes up in the air and hauls in the 35-yard catch.

videos.headline: McConaughey is hyped after Texas converts 4th down
videos.description: Matthew McConaughey is pumped for Texas after Sam Ehlinger runs for a first down on the last play of the third quarter.

videos.headline: Fourth time's the charm on Ehlinger's third rush TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger tried three previous times to run it in from short yardage but was denied, he gets in on the fourth try for his 3rd rushing touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Hardman scores after big gain from Holloman
videos.description: Jake Fromm finds Jeremiah Holloman for 31 yards then on the next play Fromm goes to Hardman for the 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Fromm finds Swift to cut Texas lead to 7
videos.description: Jake Fromm finds D'Andre Swift to cut Texas' lead in half late in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: Herman: 2018 senior class will be 'most influential' in my tenure
videos.description: Tom Herman has nothing but good things to say about his program after they take down Georgia in the Allstate Sugar Bowl.

videos.headline: Texas beats Georgia, clinches first 10-win season since 2009
videos.description: Behind Sam Ehlinger's three rushing touchdowns, Texas tops Georgia 28-21 in the Allstate Sugar Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Texas beats Georgia, clinches first 10-win season since 2009) 2019/01/01 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Ehlinger shares emotional moment with his mom
videos.description: After being named MVP of the Allstate Sugar Bowl, Texas' Sam Ehlinger heads to the stands to give his mom a hug.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ehlinger shares emotional moment with his mom) 2019/1/1 ESHEET

videos.headline: Texas' Ehlinger decrees 'we're back' after Sugar Bowl win
videos.description: Texas QB Sam Ehlinger discusses beating Georgia in the Sugar Bowl before riling up the crowd with a short message about the Longhorns' future.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Texas’ Ehlinger decrees ‘we’re back’ after Sugar Bowl win) 2019/01/01
